OL,7,FA retired police officer who left his
OL,8,Fwife to die after assaulting her and
OL,9,Fcausing her to fall down a flight of
OL,10,Fstairs has been jailed.
OL,12,FAlan Claxton was found guilty of
OL,13,Fkilling his wife Wendy, 70, after 45
OL,14,Fyears of marriage.
OL,16,FThe couple were both retired officers
OL,17,Fand lived in Gateshead.
