OL,7,FA jury at Newcastle Crown Court heard
OL,8,Fhow on the night of 30 September 2019
OL,9,Fconcerned neighbours had popped over
OL,10,Fafter noticing the front door to the
OL,11,Fcouple's home was ajar.
OL,13,FOnce inside, they found incoherent
OL,14,FClaxton slumped in a chair and his
OL,15,Fwife lying deceased on her bed
OL,16,Fupstairs.
OL,18,FWhen police arrived at the house,
OL,19,FClaxton, 74, of Hillside, Whickham,
OL,20,Fwas arrested on suspicion of murder.
