OL,7,FSenior Investigating officer,
OL,8,FDetective Chief Inspector Graeme Barr
OL,9,Fof Northumbria Police said: "Alan
OL,10,FClaxton has proven himself to be a
OL,11,Fliar throughout this investigation,
OL,12,Fgiving a number of conflicting
OL,13,Faccounts of what happened when Wendy
OL,14,Ffell, sustaining the injuries which
OL,15,Fkilled her, and I am pleased he has
OL,16,Fnow been convicted.
