OL,7,F"Claxton tried to cover up what he
OL,8,Fdid, telling us Wendy had fallen down
OL,9,Fthe stairs because she was drunk, but
OL,10,Fthe evidence we uncovered showed this
OL,11,Fto be a complete fabrication and an
OL,12,Fattempt to cover up his own callous
OL,13,Foffending.
