OL,4,Ckilling wife had history of domestic
OL,5,Cabuse
OL,7,F"The investigation established that
OL,8,FWendy had been a victim of repeated
OL,9,Falcohol-fuelled domestic violence by
OL,10,FAlan throughout their marriage.
OL,11,FTowards the end of Wendy's life she
OL,12,Fwas becoming increasingly concerned by
OL,13,Fher husband's addiction to alcohol and
OL,14,Fthe risks that this created for her.
OL,16,F"While Wendy has limited family, we
OL,17,Fknow she was a great friend to many
OL,18,Fpeople in her community and my
OL,19,Fcondolences and thoughts are with all
OL,20,Fwho knew and loved her at this
OL,21,Fdifficult time."
