OL,7,FDet Chief Insp Barr added: "I'd like
OL,8,Fto thank all the officers and staff,
OL,9,Fand criminal justice partners who
OL,10,Fhelped with this complex investigation
OL,11,Fand have helped us secure justice for
OL,12,FWendy.
OL,14,F"Domestic abuse, no matter the form it
OL,15,Ftakes, is completely unacceptable and
OL,16,Fwe are committed to putting
OL,17,Fperpetrators before the courts."
